Return

Subprog AS_NBINT
Local Decimal BASPAG
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
## Action STD
Call AS_NBINT From SUBITG
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog C_NBINT
Local Decimal BASPAG
